name: Visible Thoughts: 006
description:
006 of the Visible Thoughts series.

I'm surprised these journal pages sell so quickly. Even the ones that are priced higher have been bought a couple times. I guess there's something to say about the power of thought and its ability to ground you in the world. It makes you think separate from yourself but integrates within you as if they were words from your own mouth. There's always magnitude in strings of letters; like atoms forming the universe, each letter compounds on itself. That's a pretty special thing, don't you think?
